theorem Topology.iterate_closure_interior_succ
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    ∀ n : ℕ,
      ((fun S : Set X => closure (interior S))^[n.succ]) A =
        closure (interior A) := by
  intro n
  induction n with
  | zero =>
      simp
  | succ n ih =>
      have h_fix :
          closure (interior (closure (interior A))) = closure (interior A) := by
        simpa using
          Topology.closure_interior_closure_interior_eq_closure_interior
            (X := X) (A := A)
      simpa [Function.iterate_succ_apply', ih, h_fix]
